{"tid":1132564,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"巴西每年過千男士切除陰莖　總統震驚：因缺乏用水及肥皂","createTime":"2019-04-30T11:40:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T08:29:21.000Z","uid":68607,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b5b2b858595c57ee6e267f094e1c1596958d9e7a","tid":1132564,"uid":68607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6vRufp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6vRufp.png&h=64ddc4cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男人最痛算哪種？這肯定是其中一種。<br />\n<br />\n有「巴西特朗普」之稱的總統博爾索納羅（Jair Bolsonaro）上周四（25日）表示，巴西每年有1000名以上男性接受切除生殖器官手術，當中有部分是因欠缺基本衞生習慣以致必須去勢；對於這項數字，他表示既震驚且難過。<br />\n<br />\n博爾索納羅視察教育部之後對記者稱：「由於巴西缺乏用水及肥皂，導致每年有多達1000名男性必須切除陰莖」。他強調，政府必須與高危男性合作，使他們意識到不衛生的危險。<br />\n<br />\n巴西泌尿科學會（Brazilian Urology Society）解釋，有關數據是根據陰莖截肢病例的官方統計數據，相關男性之所以須切除陰莖，大多是因為患上癌症或愛滋病的併發症。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aavmRtW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaavmRtW.png&h=f5ee101a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n博爾索納羅：博爾索納羅言行一貫出位，他上周四（25日）表示，巴西每年有1000名以上男性男性接受切除生殖器手術，當中部分是因欠缺基本衞生習慣。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n語出驚人又低級趣味<br />\n<br />\n博爾索納羅經常語出驚人，他曾發表歧視黑人、女性等言論，惹起不少爭議。2019年3月，他在Twitter分享一段不雅影片，片中兩男子在嘉年華扭腰擺臀，隨後一人在對方頭上便溺。這位總統還問道：「甚麼是黃金浴」？此舉觸發民眾怒火，遭到國內口誅筆伐。<br />\n<br />\n雖然未知博爾索納羅所言之中，有多少男性是因為衛生習慣欠佳而去勢，但無論如何，安全性行為及保持衛生確是男士們重要的課題。"},{"pid":"659ec589bb1736ea25133dfd2e062def77616519","tid":1132564,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"post錯台?<br />\n講人類身體應該去<span style=\"color: gold;\">健康台</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e532b71b92525e7fc60a09e5a2810678962bf8b","tid":1132564,"uid":84006,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"659ec589bb1736ea25133dfd2e062def77616519","tid":1132564,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"post錯台?<br />\n講人類身體應該去<span style=\"color: gold;\">健康台</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:09:49.000Z","msg":"陰莖未硬件囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec26605080ea26a102fd9a61bc6d69220a336176","tid":1132564,"uid":75156,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"9e532b71b92525e7fc60a09e5a2810678962bf8b","tid":1132564,"uid":84006,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"659ec589bb1736ea25133dfd2e062def77616519","tid":1132564,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"post錯台?<br />\n講人類身體應該去<span style=\"color: gold;\">健康台</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:09:49.000Z","msg":"陰莖未硬件囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:19:17.000Z","msg":"樓主個條軟件黎<br />\n都係去錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73c5ce461489e66c11c9a96157e4ef811e073220","tid":1132564,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9e532b71b92525e7fc60a09e5a2810678962bf8b","tid":1132564,"uid":84006,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"659ec589bb1736ea25133dfd2e062def77616519","tid":1132564,"uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:51:53.000Z","msg":"post錯台?<br />\n講人類身體應該去<span style=\"color: gold;\">健康台</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:09:49.000Z","msg":"陰莖未硬件囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T12:40:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">健康台 = 人體硬件台</span></span>"},{"pid":"86f97f68bb89f9ee9373fefc0d05536b1cfaede4","tid":1132564,"uid":69289,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T13:01:33.0